These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, peas, plum, lemon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, house, jazz, metal
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, indian, australian
4 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, pony, goldfish
 1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of house##1
 2. the person eating zucchini is in an even position##4
 3. the argentine is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 4. the indian is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 6. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 7. the chinese is the person eating plum##1
 8. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the goldfish and the fan of metal##2
10. the person eating zucchini is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the fan of jazz is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | plum  | zucchini    | lemon    | peas   |
| Music-Genre   | house     | salsa   | jazz       | metal    |
| Nationality   | chinese | argentine | australian    | indian |
| Pet           | lizard | goldfish       | goat | pony     |

