.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, lemon, apple, broccoli
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, fishing, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, german, french, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, handball, cricket, badminton
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
 2. the german is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 4. the person eating lemon is the indonesian##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 6. the indonesian is on the left or right of the french##3
 7. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 8. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 9. the french is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
11. the french is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | plum  | lemon    | apple     | broccoli       |
| Hobby         | fishing | rock-climbing | filmmaking   | gardening |
| Nationality   | french | indonesian   | german   | argentine    |
| Sport         | cricket | badminton  | skateboarding | handball   |

