.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, cola, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, freelancer, dancer, police-officer
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, japanese, french, mexican
4 different pets are kept: rat, horse, turtle, cat
 1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 2. the japanese is the dancer##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 4. the dressmaker is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person drinking milk is the police-officer##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the mexican##1
 8. the police-officer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the australian##1
10. the owner of the rat is the person drinking cola##1
11. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | tea | cola   | almond-milk    | milk      |
| Job           | dancer | dressmaker | freelancer | police-officer     |
| Nationality   | japanese      | mexican   | australian   | french |
| Pet           | cat         | rat       | turtle  | horse       |

