.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: onion, raspberry, pumpkin, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, board-games, puzzles, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, basketball, handball, baseball
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating onion##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 9. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
11. the person drinking coffee is the person eating pomegranate##1
12. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk       | coffee   | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate   |
| Food       | raspberry        | pomegranate | onion    | pumpkin       |
| Hobby      | fishing | board-games    | puzzles  | collecting |
| Sport      | basketball  | handball  | weightlifting | baseball    |

