.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, peas, mango, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, board-games, card-games, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, software-developer, videographer, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, rowing, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person eating avocado##2
 3. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 4. the software-developer is the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the pilot is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating peas is the pilot##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is the software-developer##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
10. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | mango    | avocado      | eggplant          | peas    |
| Hobby   | board-games | video-games       | card-games | cooking |
| Job     | paramedic     | videographer      | software-developer     | pilot |
| Sport   | soccer   | swimming | rowing        | lacrosse   |

