 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 3. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 5. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of jazz is between the malaysian and the fan of funk##2
 7. the fan of indie is the person eating peach##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating peach##1
 9. the japanese is on the far right##1
10. the french is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | soy-milk    | mirinda       | fanta       |
| Food          | kale    | peach | corn | grapes     |
| Music-Genre   | country | indie        | jazz    | funk   |
| Nationality   | french  | malaysian      | british    | japanese |

