There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, italian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: goat, pony, goldfish, frog
 1. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the goldfish##2
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the egyptian is on the right of the italian##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the chinese##1
 9. the owner of the goat is between the brazilian and the person watching horror movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
