.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, broccoli, cabbage, apricot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, scientific, martial-arts, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, salsa, ambient, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, badminton, biathlon, sailing
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person watching scientific movies and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
13. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | pumpkin     | cabbage      | apricot  | broccoli        |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | martial-arts | musical | epic      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | dubstep        | gospel        | ambient        |
| Sport         | sailing | cycling    | badminton      | biathlon |

