 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person eating radish is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

