.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, almond-milk, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, camping, woodworking, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, spy, thriller, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, biathlon, tennis, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
10. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk       | cola | tea        | water        |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | woodworking       | dancing | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | spy        | adventure    | thriller      |
| Sport         | biathlon     | tennis    | weightlifting | skateboarding   |

