.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, disco, gospel, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, german, egyptian, indian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, snowboarding, golf, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, trike, roller
 1. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is between the pakistani and the indian##2
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the german##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 8. the indian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
10. the pakistani is in an even position##4
11. the pakistani is on the far right##1
12. the fan of r&b is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | r&b | punk     | gospel        |
| Nationality   | egyptian | indian  | german     | pakistani |
| Sport         | snowboarding    | climbing | golf      | tennis |
| Transport     | roller | tram     | trike | ship       |

 